data.value: The Porsche Cayenne is a luxury crossover SUV that Porsche has been manufacturing since 2002. It's available in two body styles: SUV and Coupé. The SUV is practical and adventurous, while the Coupé is sleek and dramatic with a silhouette similar to the Porsche 911. This mid-size, two-row luxury crossover is unnaturally light on its feet, with chassis tuning derived from over two decades of performance-SUV supremacy
